<p>*   Bidirectional indexing (entityâ†’messages, messageâ†’entities)<br />*   Two-phase artifact extraction:<br />    *   Phase 1: Runtime annotations (from the chat itself if AI noted them)<br />    *   Phase 2: Historical analysis (Claude searches for missed items)<br />*   Schema-driven extensibility<br />*   Error handling that escalates only when needed<br />*   Hazel rules need a home in the repo</p>
