<p>Revised Structure<br />-----------------</p>
<p>   10_chats/<br />    â”œâ”€â”€ 00_incoming/              # Automator/Hazel drop zone<br />    â”œâ”€â”€ 10_raw/                   # Git subtree<br />    â”‚   â””â”€â”€ chat-histories/<br />    â”œâ”€â”€ 20_staged/<br />    â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ pending/              # Awaiting Phase 1 extraction<br />    â”‚   â””â”€â”€ analysis_queue/       # Awaiting Phase 2 (historical sweep)<br />    â”œâ”€â”€ 30_processed/<br />    â”‚   â””â”€â”€ {source}/YYYY/MM/{chat-id}/<br />    â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ chat.json<br />    â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ meta.yaml<br />    â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ phase1/           # Runtime annotations (if present)<br />    â”‚       â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ personas.jsonl      # Line-delimited for append<br />    â”‚       â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ memories.jsonl<br />    â”‚       â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ decisions.jsonl<br />    â”‚       â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ todos.jsonl<br />    â”‚       â”‚   â””â”€â”€ discussions.jsonl<br />    â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ phase2/           # Historical analysis<br />    â”‚       â”‚   â””â”€â”€ {same structure, plus audit trail}<br />    â”‚       â””â”€â”€ issues/           # Only created if problems found<br />    â”‚           â””â”€â”€ needs_review.yaml<br />    â”œâ”€â”€ 40_artifacts/<br />    â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ indexes/<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ tags/<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ forward.sqlite     # tag â†’ [messages]<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ reverse.sqlite     # message â†’ [tags]<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ heatmap.json       # frequency data<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ personas/<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ changes.sqlite     # persona<em>update â†’ source</em>messages<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ memories/<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ decisions/<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ todos/<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ discussions/<br />    â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ pending_updates/      # Phase 2 discoveries awaiting core merge<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ personas/<br />    â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ memories/<br />    â”