<p>      - type: conflict<br />        artifact: memory<br />        phase: 2<br />        details: &quot;Phase 1 says &#x27;user prefers Python&#x27;, Phase 2 found &#x27;user prefers JavaScript&#x27;&quot;<br />        phase1<em>ref: {msg</em>idx: 42}<br />        phase2<em>ref: {msg</em>idx: 89}</p>
<p>      - type: missing<em>expected</em>artifact<br />        expected: code<em>snippet</em>auth_handler<br />        referenced<em>in: {msg</em>idx: 104}</p>
<p>    action<em>required: manual</em>review<br />    priority: medium</p>
